rComments: Very approachable and genuinely cares for the student's success.

Tracey Bowen is an amazing prof & passionate about teaching. If you put in the work you will do well in any course she teaches. The workload can be intense, but manageable as long as you stay on top of it. Extremely approachable and cares about whether or not her students are learning. Would jump at the opportunity to have her again. (Also CCT304)

very knowledgeable in her field of study, has great ideas, never boring, such a sweet sweet lady, would take her class again in a heartbeat!  incredibly caring and helpful, so compassionate and understanding, was there for me through the WORSTTT of times! what an amazing human being! keep it up dr. professor. bowen! YOURE THE MAN haha ;) ;)THNK U

very good prof, highly recommend taking her, made the course interesting and innovative, made more friends in this class than any other since it's very interactive and team-work related, also on a sidenote, i was very sick and had a family emergency resulting in me submitting my final assignment late, and she was very understanding and kind
